{"tid":210426,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iOS 版 WhatsApp 2.17.20 更新！","createTime":"2017-04-21T02:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T05:35:23.000Z","uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"131b3271d372955592cfae0c60397f58a1f70928","tid":210426,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:34:24.000Z","msg":"今晨 iOS 版 WhatsApp 更新 2.17.20 版本，今次的版本除了有介面的改變，還更新了一個免開 App 懶人新功能。<br />\n<br />\n這個免開 App 懶人新功能，就是讓 Siri 閱讀訊息，在 iOS 10.3 或以後的裝置按實 Home 鍵打開 Siri，說出「WhatsApp 閱讀訊息」，如果你有新訊息未檢視， Siri 就會將訊息閱讀一次，並會詢問你是否回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a171v70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa171v70.png&h=5e81a6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除 Siri 閱讀 WhatsApp 訊息之外，今晨 WhatsApp 更新還有 3 個要點：<br />\n<br />\n-改善通話、聯絡人資訊和群組資訊的介面，使其更整潔直覺<br />\n-在「我的更新」的頁面上你可以選擇轉發或刪除多個動態<br />\n-新增支援波斯語介面<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m712dAN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm712dAN.png&h=bb7643e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0E99Sw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0E99Sw.png&h=ba3ceb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">個相機幾撚時收返埋佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"054f4f084b048dc046bcffb6c7e42d7558a33cc2","tid":210426,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:37:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母幾時寫watch apps 呀<br />\nOn撚鳩鳩"},{"pid":"b0046bf23dfaff997a955a86319b4ad43e6057fb","tid":210426,"uid":3614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"淨係更新啲無用嘅功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80765734ea990f68f6ef6fc8b56cde8879c3658","tid":210426,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:43:06.000Z","msg":"個status 都冇人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73de6bc416daecf7d99bf49236903df1cc7edeaa","tid":210426,"uid":28412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母幾時寫watch apps 呀<br />\nOn撚鳩鳩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都等咗好耐，出咁耐都未有一個正正式式嘅app <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7894824f91ee15c53e9f101fccedf3757ccc8033","tid":210426,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"我想問下有邊個會用siri黎睇訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d672981a998f99e62f82fef9be50e461785b58a","tid":210426,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"呢個功能好on9"},{"pid":"fb234d53eafa023f1e3b555425972be6ec7537a4","tid":210426,"uid":8153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問下有邊個會用siri黎睇訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n揸緊車掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}